---
// About Section
---

<section id="about" class="section">
  <h2 class="section-title">About</h2>
  <div class="about-content">
    <p>
      My name is <strong>Chaidir Ali Assegaf</strong>. I am a software developer skilled in various programming languages and frameworks,
      with extensive experience in famous ERP systems.
    </p>
    <p>
      I specialize in <a href="https://dynamics.microsoft.com/" target="_blank" class="link">Microsoft Dynamics</a> ecosystem development,
      including Dynamics AX 2012 R3, Dynamics 365 Finance and Operations, Dynamics 365 Business Central, PowerApps, and Power Automate.
      My expertise spans across multiple technologies including C#, X++, TypeScript, JavaScript, PHP, and modern web frameworks like Blazor, React, and Laravel.
    </p>
    <p>
      Throughout my career, I have delivered custom ERP solutions, data integration projects, and enterprise applications
      for various industries, helping businesses optimize their operations through tailored software solutions.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .section {
    margin-bottom: 6rem;
    scroll-margin-top: 4rem;
  }

  .section-title {
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 10;
    backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    background-color: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.8);
    padding: 1.5rem 0;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--slate-200);
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .section-title {
      display: none;
    }
  }

  .about-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .about-content p {
    color: var(--slate-400);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .link {
    color: var(--slate-200);
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: color 0.2s ease;
    position: relative;
  }

  .link:hover {
    color: var(--teal-300);
  }

  .link::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    width: 0;
    height: 1px;
    bottom: -2px;
    left: 0;
    background-color: var(--teal-300);
    transition: width 0.2s ease;
  }

  .link:hover::after {
    width: 100%;
  }
</style>
